                     <interp inst="t18160214-84-person955" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner had a lodging at our house, on the 24th of January, and on his coming down stairs between nine and ten o'clock the next morning; I asked him to stay until somebody went up stairs to see that all was left right. He said he would, but the moment I turned my back, he made his escape out of the door. I followed him, and stopped him, and took the sheer and blanket from him.</p>
